@baseUrl = http://localhost:8089/api
@token = your_access_token_here

### ==========================================
### 4. CART (/api/cart)
### ==========================================

### Lấy giỏ hàng
GET {{baseUrl}}/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Lấy số lượng giỏ hàng
GET {{baseUrl}}/cart/count
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Thêm vào giỏ hàng
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": 1
}

### Xóa khỏi giỏ hàng
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cart/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Xóa toàn bộ giỏ hàng
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
